ComicInfo.Title: Artificial Intelligence Part 2
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: Artificial Intelligence Part 2: Alpha 001 places Destro and Baroness under its control. Sean is spotted by Cobra surveillance, convincing them that the original Snake Eyes is still alive. Sightline's new leg contains a tracking device which Mainframe removes, intending to use it to send Cobra false intelligence.
